node.text:
We are so excited to deliver some awesome news for you soon! Make sure to follow @bandainamcous & @bandaihobbyus for whats happening this week during Gundam Online Expo 2021 on Gundam.info Official Youtube Channel!

#gundam #gunpla

Virtual Crunchyroll Expo was such a blast. Being able to host it for the second year in a row was insane. I want to give a huge shout out to the most awesome cohost I could ever ask for Mario @emp_maniac , we work so well together so it ran smooth as butter 😉 It also was just made better by the production and contestants amazing cosplays and performances! I’m so proud of the cosplay community as a whole that night. You all are amazing! Also being able to just fully be endorsing Gundam products is literally a dream come true. Let’s freaking go Mecha Fans! Thank you @crunchyrollexpo @crunchyroll for being for legit and all about the fans since day 1! 

#vcrx #gundam #asus #crunchroll

node.text:
I am so excited and honored to announce that I will be the official Host for the Gundam Breaker Battlogue & Gundam Games Panel  during Gundam Online Expo 2021 next week!

Join us, David & Xavier, and BNEA Gundam CM Nick on August 26th! 

Can’t wait to see you there!

#Gunpla #Gundam #Battlogue

node.text:
I want to give a huge thank you to @tokushoutsu @plutotv for having me be your official “Quantum” historian for Ultraman Day celebrating 55 Years of this amazing legacy! 

If you were to tell younger me this would be what I would be doing I would not believe it 😱 I’m such a huge Ultraman fan so it’s been a life long dream to take part in anything like this, let alone host. The team is insanely talented and I’m so happy it all came together 🎉

#UltramanDay #ULTRATHON
